ActivityInfo (40 bytes): </b>Contains a <b>FAX_SERVER_ACTIVITY</b> (section <a href="86c61ea7-73a5-4e3d-a8f2-a293667ebb12" data-linktype="relative-path">2.2.19</a>) structure that
contains information about the server activity that has changed. This event
SHOULD only be sent when the message counters in the server activity structure
change. No event is sent when an event log entry is added on the server.</p>
